.  field definitions for standard input routines
.------------------------------------------------ 
.  
.  standard input parameters  
.----------------------------
ROW       FORM     2   *  row for input to occur
COL       FORM     2   *  column for input to occur
MODE      FORM     1   *  0 = add mode. allow sceen movement
.                      *  1 = modify mode. no screen movement
.                      *      and ok prompt at end of input
DEFFLAG   FORM     1   *  0 = must not default to null
.                      *  1 = default of null allowed
.  standard output parameter
.----------------------------
INFLAG    FORM     1   *  0 = no screen movement
.                      *  1 = move to previous input
.                      *  2 = move to next input
.                      *  3 = exit * entered    
.  standard working variables
.-----------------------------
SP12      INIT     "            " 
SP13      INIT     "             " 
NEXT      INIT     ">"
LAST      INIT     "<"
EXITA     INIT     "*"
